# placeholders: (no placeholders)
breed_no_pairs: No breeding pairs in this room.

# placeholders: (no placeholders)
breed_all_young: The pairs in this room are still too young to breed. Select one to see how long until they're ready.

# placeholders: (no placeholders)
breed_all_resting: All breeding pairs are resting after a recent litter. Try again later.

# placeholders: (no placeholders)
